# Folder Structure (Hard Rule)

- **app/** — Routes, layouts, loading/error UI; no business logic.
- **components/** — Presentational/container; **components/ui/** = shadcn only.
- **lib/** — Pure functions, types, constants (e.g. `canvasParser.ts`, `prompts.ts`); no side effects.
- **stores/** — Zustand only; immutable updates.
- **services/** — Side effects (Supabase, fetch); return `Result<T,E>`; test-injectable; no Bedrock in client.
- **supabase/migrations/** — Migration files; apply via CLI.
- API routes under **app/api/** (e.g. `app/api/chat/route.ts`); no top-level `api/`.
